headline: Stock Market Today: AmEx rises as stocks look to regain footing
summary: The polite term is that stocks are mixed Friday. It means this for now: The Dow Jones Industrial Average is higher, thanks in part to gains for American Express, pushing toward a 4% gain, because its core customers — the affluent — are doing what they do: They're continuing to spend. ...
